  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study we investigate the following properties of the transversus abdominis plane
      block in healthy volunteers:

        1. Cutaneous analgesic distribution

        2. Muscular affection

        3. Reproducibility
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
